OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fwith clear spells and light winds
OL,7,Fleading to a touch of frost. A band of
OL,8,Fcloud and the odd shower will move
OL,9,Feast for a time overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,12,Fa frost in places. It will remain dry
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunshine but perhaps
OL,14,Fsome high cloud spreading east in the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
